name: Dogira
public_notice: Dogira has migrated to Polygon Network. Total Supply was rebased to a factor of 1:10 during the contract migration. Read more at: https://dogira-team.medium.com/september-medium-update-fe4a891f8bb9
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
